### § 1.5 Term of the agreement

This data processing agreement applies for the term of the underlying main
contract, or for as long as the Processor processes personal data of the
Controller. It ends automatically upon termination of the main contract and the
complete return or deletion of the data pursuant to § 7. A separate termination
of the DPA is not required.

